<plot>A major TV channel correspondent Sasha Potapova loses everything at once: dear job, handsome husband, confidence in future. Moreover, her close friend TV anchorman Ivan disappears in the Chechnya's war zone. Desperate Sasha turns for help to a stranger - a French journalist Philip Beauvais who came to Moscow to write a book about Russia. Sasha has no idea what adventures and discoveries she is going to experience with that man.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?379246</url></doc>
